<br>
I think that the &quot;goal&quot; is to kill uber mob X as far at the blue servers go. But the purpose of that goal is to get the PHAT LOOTZ that uber mob X drops. The purpose of getting the PHAT LOOTZ is to make your stats better so yur able to kill the even more uber mob Y. So single boxers goal is to max their stats basically, through AA and Gear.<br>
<br>
One way to compare toons is raw stats, another is by pvp, another might be total DPS, or possibly whats the highest level mob you can kill.<br>
<br>
But when you use these measures to compare one toon to multiple toons the one toon almost always will lose, espically if its raw Stats X 6 or 1v6 pvp or total DPS... <br>
<br>
Sure if you say &quot;who is the best guild leader in the game&quot; Furor would be way up there and I would not even be on the list, but the reason he is a guild leader - to kill Uber Mob X to get its PHAT LOOTZ to improve his stats - I beat him becuase my stats or my pvp power or my total dps or my ability to kill higher level mobs then him is greater because I have 6 level 65 toons. <br>
<br>
Sabok is even better than me because the total stats or total dps or his total pvp power (well dont know for sure on that one) or his ability to solo mobs higher then me is better then me. <br>
<br>
I think the fairest comparison is &quot;What is the highest level mob you can kill solo using accounts that you own playing all the toons yourself at the same time.&quot; That brings the PvPers into the PvE world for comparison. Right now I did a level 65, which isn't all that good but I will only get better. Still its better than what Furor can do, but much worse then Sabok. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=throes>Throes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Flintnilf the Wise</span><br>  Posts: 336<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/24/03 6:57 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: OH Snaps NOOOTZ DOWNZORS!</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>It shows how desperate and unstable you are, chosing to jump on bandwagons with people like Tomb and Sam just to flame me<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
